Title: A Key Element
Description:
<This orb of earth thrums with energy.>

<Elementalist Taiyang might know what to do with it.>
ObjectivesText: Return the Orb of Primal Stone to Elementalist Taiyang in the Life Vault Ruins.
RewardText: I can feel the elemental energy stored within this orb. You may have found a solution to our troubles here.
